		""
		"&6Mr Beardstone&r has done a video on how to make one, feel free to check it out"
	]
	quest.156AA919AC78D534.quest_subtitle: "Vertical travel"
	quest.17D3020E559009E3.quest_desc: [
		"When you place the &6water wheel&r you can flow water over it to start producing stress units, it will produce the same stress whether 1 or more sides are covered in water"
		""
		"You can change the aesthetic of the water wheel by right clicking it with a plank and it will appear like that plank type"
	]
	quest.17D3020E559009E3.quest_subtitle: "A method of generation stress"
	quest.18736449E1AADBCD.quest_desc: ["The &6brass casing&r is the upgrade of the &eandesite casing&r with it's ability to make better quality items for automation"]
	quest.18736449E1AADBCD.quest_subtitle: "The next generation of casing"
	quest.187518D514B536F4.quest_desc: ["The train controls are the block that is needed to allow your train to move once it's assembled. If you put 2 &6train controls&r in a single train then the train will be able to travel in both directions "]
	quest.187518D514B536F4.quest_subtitle: "Make a train move"
	quest.1AB5695E3FFA5338.title: "Make a &dNetherite Ingot&r"
	quest.1ABAF66FF1313E57.quest_desc: ["The &6hose pulley&r has the ability to pull liquids from the world to be transported, if the source the pulley is pulling from is larger than 10,000 blocks then it classes it as an infinite source of liquid"]
	quest.1ABAF66FF1313E57.quest_subtitle: "Moving Liquid"
	quest.1AC0EC7056C0DCD4.quest_subtitle: "Craft any drawer"
	quest.1AF4019667A352B1.quest_desc: ["The &6trim&r is a really handy utility block within the mod. It is used to link up drawers to eachother when they don't directly touch, it's pretty much a fake drawer as it cannot store any items within it but is still part of your total drawer network"]
	quest.1AF4019667A352B1.quest_subtitle: "Connect drawer without worrying of loosing items into them"
	quest.1AFE8D1CE55C1527.title: "Enter a &dBastion&r"
