	quest.2DCF9C41FA7D28E4.quest_desc: ["The &6train station&r is the part that makes trains work. You can create a train from within gui of the train station. It's other job is as the place where the train will stop along a route, these are the place you enter into the &etrain schedule&r as the stopping locations"]
	quest.2DCF9C41FA7D28E4.quest_subtitle: "Waypoints for trains"
	quest.2E232FE3E08A0E7F.quest_desc: ["You can place &6large cogwheels&r at 90 degrees to eachother and it will change the direction of rotation"]
