	quest.34CF8CC6400ACAB7.title: "Windmill Bearing"
	quest.35B96F4A231FE50E.quest_subtitle: "Collect a melon slice"
	quest.35BB0498DD5DC544.quest_desc: [
		"&bHyper enchanting&r let's you go above the normal enchantment limit in the base game."
		""
		"To be able to mix it you will need to super heart a &6blaze burner below the basin and mixer&r you do this by feeding the &6blaze burner&r a blaze cake. You will get 10% of the liquid xp back in &bhyper experience liquid&r"
		""
		"You can pump the &bhyper experience liquid&r into the blaze enchanter and then give when enchanting it will enchant the tool 1 level higher than the book given to the &6blaze enchanter&r"
	]
	quest.35BB0498DD5DC544.quest_subtitle: "In a mixer you need liquid xp, a lapis and a glow ink sac"
	quest.36057360ADDD3B23.title: "Obtain a &eDune Armour Trim&r"
	quest.3612EB73B9709015.quest_desc: ["The &6precision mechanism&r is used in making some more advanced items like the &6rotational speed controller&r and it requires a gold sheet to have 3 items deployed onto it in a specific order of small cogwheel then large cogwheel and lastely an iron nugget. That process is repeated 5x and has an 80% chance to work at the end"]
	quest.3612EB73B9709015.quest_subtitle: "Used in some crafting recipes"
	quest.3686BAC07C9F5E22.title: "Make a crafting table"
	quest.39AD444F5F568CC9.quest_subtitle: "The key to show or hide quanity on drawers"
	quest.39E6CA577F59AB93.quest_subtitle: "Destroys items when the draw gets full"
	quest.3A1FD20417D15F80.quest_desc: ["&6Super glue&r is the key part of all create multi blocks as it makes sure all the parts stay as one when the machine is started"]
	quest.3A1FD20417D15F80.quest_subtitle: "Getting stuck in"
