	quest.4A9D0D014C61CB7B.quest_subtitle: "The start of the great railways"
	quest.4AD661C0A10ABD3B.quest_desc: ["With a spout attached to the tank of liquid xp via pipes, you will be able to put the liquid back into bottles either by right clicking bottles onto a depot or having bottles put on a belt line underneath the spout"]
