	quest.4D55A7ABD7557FF1.quest_desc: ["Any &6enchanted item&r can be placed on a disenchanted and it will take the xp and store it as liquid and you will get what you put that was enchanted back, so &6enchanted book&r will give you a book back, or &6an enchanted piece of armour&r will give you the armour piece without any enchantments"]
	quest.4D55A7ABD7557FF1.quest_subtitle: "Any enchanted book"
