	quest.4DE18CB6F344809A.title: "Make a fully powered beacon"
	quest.4EA5BE7A1FC1C75E.title: "Locate a &bShipwreck&r"
	quest.4F4415CE4EC30024.quest_desc: ["The &6fluid tank&r is a easy way to store a large amount of liquid. The biggest it can be is a 3x3 base and upto 30 tall, which stores a crazy amount"]
	quest.4F4415CE4EC30024.quest_subtitle: "A large liquid container"
	quest.4F603085044BFAAD.title: "Obtain a &2Shaper Armour Trim&r"
	quest.4FFE92F9BD1FA9F9.quest_desc: ["The &62x2 drawer&r holds &68 stacks&r in each of the option slots"]
	quest.4FFE92F9BD1FA9F9.quest_subtitle: "What it holds"
	quest.5062F049AFCBC5CB.quest_desc: ["You will polish the &drose quartz&r to use in making electron tubes"]
	quest.5062F049AFCBC5CB.quest_subtitle: "Off hand the sand paper and then right click with the &drose quartz&r"
	quest.5062F049AFCBC5CB.title: "&dPolished Rose Quartz&r"
	quest.51E37CE8D0904957.title: "Locate a &2Pillager Outpost&r"
	quest.53BB590289D14A36.quest_desc: ["The &6disenchanter&r has the ability to take enchants off of armour and store the xp it collects as liquid xp that can then be solidified to be consumed to be used again, it will be really helpful to have at a mob farm for armour drops. Standing on a &6disenchanter&r will take levels from the player and turn them into liquid"]
	quest.53BB590289D14A36.quest_subtitle: "Liquid xp?"
	quest.53D1F8DFB89185AF.title: "Obtain a &5Spire Armour Trim&r"
	quest.54C243CD0E3D8F80.quest_desc: ["&6Andesite funnels&r are used to pull items out of a chest one at a time, they will drop the items onto a &6belt&r or &6depot&r below it"]
	quest.54C243CD0E3D8F80.quest_subtitle: "Crafted with andesite alloy and dried kelp"
	quest.54C243CD0E3D8F80.title: "Andesite Funnel"
	quest.5562F1C4EAEE40B3.quest_subtitle: "Collect a carrot"
	quest.56BE267CE6F7C4F9.quest_desc: ["When placing an &6Enchanted golden apple&r onto a &6disenchanter&r it will remove the enchanted aspect and give you a &eregular golden apple&r back and store the xp as liquid xp, that xp can be tranfered into a tank for later storage"]
	quest.56BE267CE6F7C4F9.quest_subtitle: "Notch Apple"
	quest.56BE267CE6F7C4F9.title: "Disenchanting Enchanted Golden Apples"
	quest.5720A87944651114.quest_subtitle: "The labels glow in the dark"
	quest.57BACA91541F39D0.quest_subtitle: "Gives a redstone signal based on how full the drawer is"
	quest.59AEBA331EE4F644.quest_desc: ["The &6steam engine&r is a way to produce stress units using heat and water. When placing a &6steam engine&r on the side of a &efluid tank&r that's full of water and has a heat source below it it will start to create rotational force. The higher the heat source the faster the &6steam engine&r will move. The best source for the highest output is &eblaze burners&r being fed blaze cakes to super heat the water tank. At the highest level you can add 8 &6steam engines&r to the tank."]
	quest.59AEBA331EE4F644.quest_subtitle: "A different stress unit source"
	quest.5A7B1CB5FB1E7D0C.quest_subtitle: "Make a shovel"
	quest.5A7B1CB5FB1E7D0C.title: "The dirt destroyer"
